title: Haggard Wulf - Live At WCLG Studio's Punk And Ska Show [FLAC]
description:
Haggard Wulf are a 2-piece band from Morgantown, WV, who bring together
a mixture of blues, rockabilly and punk rock. Their sound and style is
diverse, bringing a very full sound to the table. They have a very strong DIY
ethic, much like the punk bands of the late 70s and early 80s.

This 5 track album was recorded live at 100.1 FM WCLG studios for the Punk And Ska Show on June 25, 2012.

Tracklist:

1. The Shadow Knows (3:40)
2. Interview (Part 1) (5:43)
3. Children Of The Grave (3:44)
4. Interview (Part 2) (4:18)
5. The Floorboards (2:32)
